    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RHI prediction accuracy within 10% acceptance threshold across all 5 operating points. The 6 non-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The validation campaign was conducted under solver build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which the team assessed as effectively equivalent to the registered production build ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7 based on vendor release notes indicating no functional code changes between the rc2 tag and the final release. On this basis the credibility package is accepted and the model is cleared for COU1 use.",
